    SpringObjenesis
    Spring-specific variant of ObjenesisStd / ObjenesisBase, providing a cache based on Class keys instead of class names, and allowing for selective use of the cache.

程序包org.springframework.objenesis的说明

Spring's repackaging of Objenesis 2.1 (for internal use only).

This repackaging technique avoids any potential conflicts with dependencies on different Objenesis versions at the application level or from third-party libraries and frameworks.

As this repackaging happens at the class file level, sources and javadocs are not available here. See the original Objenesis docs for details when working with these classes.
